thread.title: Dan Gausepohl

author: Dan Gausepohl
title: Dan Gausepohl
text:
Good service and communication for shipping. My concern was an apparent wound at the base of the tree that was obviously from rough
handling. Spring is just around the corner and time will tell if the Asian Pear tree will survive. The packaging itself was done with care and the directions included where good. I hope to order from Willis Orchard again.
